channel.title: Just read if you know about delta clients
channel.description:
Dudes, ive portforwarded my router and everything...Got rid of hamachi but then i went to jar and sign so i could get my webclient done. i jared and signed it fine but then when i double click the client.jar is doesnt open at all.
anyone who knows how to fix this please please take 5 mins and help me.
Thanks
